articles.title: Australia Foreign Minister Penny Wong Marries Longtime Partner, Shares Pic - NDTV
articles.description: Australia's Foreign Minister Penny Wong, the country's first openly gay female parliamentarian, has married her partner Sophie Allouache, Wong said on Sunday.
